#X text 61 73 Allpass filters can be used in series to implement a reverb model. The [rev1~] abstraction that comes with Pd Vanilla uses 10 stages of allpass filters in series. It's a very simple reverb with only a decay parameter \, which indicates how much dB the output has after 1 second in percentage of dB. Check its help file., f 55;
